mediate/massive galaxies in more\nmassive haloes. At stellar masses lower than $\\log M_* \\lesssim 9.5$ both\nquenching mechanisms become inefficient, independently of the redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2020 02:48:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2020 06:52:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
