 abundances simultaneously only if we assume\nthat long-period binaries are favored at [Fe/H] < -3.5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2020 06:29:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
